187
00:12:16,882 --> 00:12:18,582
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau akan punya anak, Pengacara Eun.</font>

188
00:12:18,582 --> 00:12:20,082
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak ingin anak sepertinya.</font>

189
00:12:20,082 --> 00:12:21,512
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?
Kenapa?</font>

190
00:12:21,782 --> 00:12:23,812
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada apa denganku?
Aku tampan...</font>

191
00:12:23,812 --> 00:12:24,882
<font color=#FFFF00>dan kaya, kau bodoh.</font>

192
00:12:24,882 --> 00:12:26,352
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku ingin uangnya saja.</font>

193
00:12:26,352 --> 00:12:27,412
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita bagi dua.</font>

194
00:12:28,552 --> 00:12:29,712
<font color=#FFFF00>Dasar...</font>

195
00:12:31,552 --> 00:12:34,682
<font color=#FFFF00>Bisakah kita sekali saja,
