196
00:12:35,082 --> 00:12:37,482
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu keinginanku saat ini, okay?</font>

197
00:12:37,512 --> 00:12:38,952
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku datang.</font>

198
00:12:38,952 --> 00:12:40,112
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa lagi? Kenapa?</font>

199
00:12:40,112 --> 00:12:41,782
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalian membuat Ji Wook kesal lagi?</font>

200
00:12:41,782 --> 00:12:43,012
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa sidangnya lancar?</font>

201
00:12:43,082 --> 00:12:44,612
<font color=#FFFF00>Tentu. Kau tahu aku.</font>

202
00:12:44,882 --> 00:12:47,182
<font color=#FFFF00>Ah, ya. Luangkan waktu kalian malam ini.</font>

203
00:12:47,512 --> 00:12:48,512
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan traktir kalian.</font>

204
00:12:49,282 --> 00:12:51,182
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku dapat sebotol wine sebagai hadiah.</font>

205
00:12:51,352 --> 00:12:52,512
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku juga punya sampanye.</font>

206
00:12:52,652 --> 00:12:55,352
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan siapkan apa pun yang kalian mau.</font>

207
00:12:55,782 --> 00:12:56,912
<font color=#FFFF00>Semuanya bisa, kan?</font>

208
00:12:56,912 --> 00:12:58,852
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku mau ke kamar mandi.</font>

209
00:12:58,852 --> 00:12:59,912
<font color=#FFFF00>Pertemuan selesai.</font>

210
00:13:00,412 --> 00:13:01,452
<font color=#FFFF00>Selesai.</font>

211
00:13:01,512 --> 00:13:02,712
<font color=#FFFF00>- Yah...
- Astaga.</font>

212
00:13:02,712 --> 00:13:03,852
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalian bisa, kan?</font>

213
00:13:06,512 --> 00:13:10,052
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau pasti tahu kenapa kau di sini sekarang.</font>

214
00:13:10,682 --> 00:13:11,712
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya.</font>

215
00:13:11,712 --> 00:13:14,182
<font color=#FFFF00>Dugaan penghancuran bukti dan sumpah palsu.</font>

216
00:13:14,912 --> 00:13:18,182
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tak yakin apa kau tahu,
