217
00:13:20,282 --> 00:13:21,382
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau begitu, kita mulai?</font>

218
00:13:37,482 --> 00:13:38,482
<font color=#FFFF00>Sebentar.</font>

219
00:13:45,052 --> 00:13:46,452
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku berpikir bahwa...</font>

220
00:13:47,182 --> 00:13:48,482
<font color=#FFFF00>...ada yang aneh.</font>

221
00:13:50,182 --> 00:13:51,282
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau menyembunyikan...</font>

222
00:13:53,052 --> 00:13:54,182
<font color=#FFFF00>...bingkai lukisan?</font>

223
00:13:56,252 --> 00:13:57,982
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada sesuatu, bukan?</font>

224
00:14:00,952 --> 00:14:02,312
<font color=#FFFF00>Sepertinya ada.</font>

225
00:14:04,182 --> 00:14:05,752
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau bisa beritahu itu, bukan?</font>

226
00:14:37,152 --> 00:14:38,452
<font color=#FFFF00>"Tapi jika seorang pria..."</font>

227
00:14:38,512 --> 00:14:40,612
<font color=#FFFF00>- "...kebetulan bertemu seorang gadis..."
