254
00:17:47,682 --> 00:17:49,952
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya. Benarkah?</font>

255
00:17:59,382 --> 00:18:00,582
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, aku mendengarkan.</font>

256
00:18:00,582 --> 00:18:03,182
<font color=#FFFF00>Senior, kenapa kau menangis seperti bayi di lorong?</font>

257
00:18:04,152 --> 00:18:07,412
