272
00:18:47,512 --> 00:18:48,982
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan minta dia berterimakasih.</font>

273
00:18:48,982 --> 00:18:50,452
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi kau akan menemuinya sendirian?</font>

274
00:18:50,452 --> 00:18:51,952
<font color=#FFFF00>- Apa tidak bisa?
- Tidak bisa.</font>

275
00:18:51,952 --> 00:18:53,512
<font color=#FFFF00>- Kenapa?
- Kita bela dia bersama.</font>

276
00:19:00,852 --> 00:19:02,352
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya ampun, maaf.</font>

277
00:19:15,452 --> 00:19:16,582
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukankah kita harus temui dia?</font>

278
00:19:20,752 --> 00:19:21,752
<font color=#FFFF00>Bersama...</font>

279
00:19:51,122 --> 00:19:52,622
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau takut naik lift?</font>

280
00:20:47,012 --> 00:20:48,052
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan...</font>

281
00:20:49,082 --> 00:20:50,182
<font color=#FFFF00>...sentuh dia.</font>

282
00:20:50,552 --> 00:20:51,582
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?</font>

283
00:20:51,782 --> 00:20:53,652
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku mengerti.</font>

284
00:20:53,712 --> 00:20:56,282
<font color=#FFFF00>Kuyakin kau butuh seseorang untuk dibenci.</font>

285
00:20:56,382 --> 00:20:58,252
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau mungkin butuh seseorang untuk disalahkan.</font>

286
00:20:59,452 --> 00:21:01,182
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi kau harusnya tidak melewati batas.</font>

287
00:21:02,182 --> 00:21:03,622
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika kau mencoba menyakitinya lagi...</font>

288
00:21:04,122 --> 00:21:06,852
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku bukan orang rendahan sepertimu,</font>

289
00:21:07,012 --> 00:21:09,122
<font color=#FFFF00>jadi aku hanya akan gunakan hukum
