290
00:21:10,152 --> 00:21:11,452
<font color=#FFFF00>aku cenderung lebih berani.</font>

291
00:21:15,382 --> 00:21:17,012
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau mengancamku lagi?</font>

292
00:21:17,412 --> 00:21:19,852
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya. Aku mengancammu.</font>

293
00:21:20,312 --> 00:21:21,622
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi dengarkan baik-baik.</font>

294
00:21:23,552 --> 00:21:25,582
<font color=#FFFF00>Sekali lagi kau sakiti Eun Bong Hee,</font>

295
00:21:31,812 --> 00:21:33,312
<font color=#FFFF00>aku akan lakukan hal yang sama padamu.</font>

296
00:21:34,952 --> 00:21:35,952
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi...</font>

297
00:21:37,382 --> 00:21:38,812
<font color=#FFFF00>...jangan sentuh dia.</font>

298
00:21:47,552 --> 00:21:48,552
<font color=#FFFF00>Ah,</font>

299
00:21:49,312 --> 00:21:52,582
<font color=#FFFF00>kau harus naik lift untuk eksekutif lain kali.</font>

300
00:21:52,982 --> 00:21:55,382
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau membuat pegawaimu merasa tidak nyaman.</font>

301
00:22:20,082 --> 00:22:22,182
<font color=#FFFF00>Eun Bong Hee, biar kujelaskan yang tadi.</font>

302
00:22:22,182 --> 00:22:23,852
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan mencampuri urusanku lagi.</font>

303
00:22:25,612 --> 00:22:27,452
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana bisa urusanmu?
