304
00:22:27,452 --> 00:22:28,452
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu urusanku,</font>

305
00:22:28,682 --> 00:22:31,412
<font color=#FFFF00>tapi juga jadi urusannu karena kau ikut campur.</font>

306
00:22:31,712 --> 00:22:34,452
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi, berhentilah di sini.</font>

307
00:22:35,452 --> 00:22:37,152
<font color=#FFFF00>- Bukan begitu.
