308
00:22:42,312 --> 00:22:43,352
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak.</font>

309
00:22:43,852 --> 00:22:45,882
<font color=#FFFF00>Bahkan jika kita tak saling kenal secara pribadi,</font>

310
00:22:46,182 --> 00:22:48,552
<font color=#FFFF00>aku akan ikut campur dan
