329
00:24:50,482 --> 00:24:54,082
<font color=#FFFF00>Seperti kataku tadi, aku akan
traktir makan malam hari ini.</font>

330
00:24:56,382 --> 00:24:57,382
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak.</font>

331
00:24:58,612 --> 00:25:00,812
<font color=#FFFF00>Semua orang masih mabuk, dan ini kacau.</font>

332
00:25:00,812 --> 00:25:02,252
<font color=#FFFF00>Semua orang tidak enak badan hari ini.</font>

333
00:25:11,182 --> 00:25:12,182
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku pikir begitu.</font>

334
00:25:22,182 --> 00:25:23,182
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga...</font>

335
00:25:23,782 --> 00:25:25,352
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalian makan kue tanpa izin dariku.</font>

336
00:25:33,752 --> 00:25:35,082
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan menangkapmu!</font>

337
00:26:11,452 --> 00:26:12,482
<font color=#FFFF00>Selamat ulang tahun,</font>

338
00:26:13,552 --> 00:26:14,552
<font color=#FFFF00>Eun Hyuk.</font>

339
00:26:19,812 --> 00:26:20,852
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah.</font>

340
00:26:31,682 --> 00:26:32,682
<font color=#FFFF00>Cha Yoo Jung.</font>

341
00:26:32,852 --> 00:26:34,012
<font color=#FFFF00>Selamat ulang tahun.</font>

342
00:26:39,852 --> 00:26:41,812
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita bertiga sering datang ke sini.</font>

343
